{"tid":819412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解平淡一生都咁難","createTime":"2018-09-14T18:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T18:41:55.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbfd7c47d909ea7ff8e4dfcddc87473c4a7df37","tid":819412,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:23:40.000Z","msg":"由細俾人打大喝罵大<br />\n讀書揾工為交差<br />\n行每一步都要諗屋企有咩反應<br />\n又驚過時過節攞出黎講會瘀<br />\n唔單止你瘀<br />\n你屋企瘀埋一份<br />\n要求唔高<br />\n成世同屋企住<br />\n溝唔溝到女唔緊要<br />\n有份aco做<br />\n有飯食有瓦遮頭就夠<br />\n唔駛ot<br />\n唔駛對客<br />\n生日join公司每月生日會<br />\n有20k個月<br />\n人生冇咩痛苦<br />\n有病自己食藥<br />\n大病睇政府<br />\n排到就排<br />\n輪唔到就死左去算<br />\n由細到大<br />\n冇大志<br />\n冇理想<br />\n冇夢想<br />\n輕輕飄過就算<br />\n但就算咁<br />\n呢個世界係都要同你過唔去"},{"pid":"40f228542de4596651018d15be75a6487dd837db","tid":819412,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"因為煩惱會自己搵你"},{"pid":"55b28c008844d597900a0fbc0cbb2cf38a32c2ae","tid":819412,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"平淡一生係香港係好多人既夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而係外國係基本"},{"pid":"e40a2add1867656f5f461640d7b78ef75b832003","tid":819412,"uid":113305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:31:22.000Z","msg":"何必將人生睇到咁辛苦呢，人生唔痛苦就唔叫人生啦<br />\n師兄你諗下大把人慘過你人地咪又係過得好開心<br />\n何必在意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c92d2b1f2f29e8e1c01ac95c21413b3e8505ed","tid":819412,"uid":146495,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}